    "opinions": [
      {
        "text": "ORDER\nPER CURIAM.\nAND NOW, this 30th day of November, 2010, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is hereby treated as a Petition for Review, as this matter involves a challenge to the Superior Court\u2019s order quashing and dismissing Petitioner\u2019s appeal. See Vaccone v. Syken, 587 Pa. 380, 899 A.2d 1103, 1106 n. 2 (2006). The order of the Superior Court is AFFIRMED.",
